<div class="legal-page">

<header>
  <div class="app-name">EDU Plus Apps</div>
  <h1>Independent Development Disclosure</h1>
  <div class="meta">EDU Mileage+ &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Last updated: April 28, 2026</div>
</header>

<main>

  <div class="info-box">
    <strong>The short version:</strong> EDU Mileage+ is an independent product
    built solely with personal resources. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by,
    or developed in cooperation with any school district or educational institution.
  </div>

  <section>
    <h2>1. Independent Product</h2>
    <p>EDU Mileage+ is an independent product. It was conceived, designed,
    developed, tested, and deployed by an individual developer acting solely in
    a personal capacity. No part of the app&rsquo;s development was performed
    within the scope of any employment, contract, or other formal relationship
    with a school district, educational institution, or other organization.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>2. Personal Resources Only</h2>
    <p>All development resources &mdash; including hardware, software licenses,
    development tools, network connectivity, and time &mdash; were personal
    resources of the developer. No equipment, software, intellectual property,
    confidential information, proprietary data, or other materials belonging to
    any school district, employer, or third party were used in the creation,
    development, testing, or operation of this product.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. No Affiliation or Endorsement</h2>
    <p>EDU Mileage+ is not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by, or
    developed in cooperation with any school district or educational institution.
    References to school district workflows or terminology in the app reflect
    general industry knowledge and are intended to make the product useful to
    educators across many districts. They do not represent the official
    practices or endorsement of any specific district.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>4. Distribution and Ownership</h2>
    <p>The app is distributed as a commercial product available to any
    individual user through the Apple App Store under standard subscription
    terms. All intellectual property in EDU Mileage+ is owned by the developer.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>5. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this disclosure can be sent to
    <a href="mailto:support@eduplusapps.com">support@eduplusapps.com</a>.</p>
  </section>

</main>

<footer class="page-footer">
  &copy; 2026 EDU Plus Apps &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
